Ruby gem for generation of image galleries

Dependencies
Rails >= 3.2

Coffee-Script
gem coffee-rails

jQuery
gem jquery-rails

Quick Start
Gemfile

gem 'hermitage'

Terminal
$ bundle
$ rails generate hermitage:install

View
render_gallery_for @images 

<%= render_gallery_for @posts, original: 'attachment(:full)', thumbnail: 'attachment(:thumbnail)' %>

# or any other array of objects with image attachments
